FS T205 Cobb American Beauty SGC 60

Waiting for one person to get back to me but the price is $3100 delivered. That is accounting for no premium on the tougher American Beauty back. There are a ton of sales in this grade and this is in the lower to middle price of a common back. Centered nicely for the series....
Your about $1500 shy of what I think it's worth:confused:.  Nice card
